<p>UCS Profiles is UCS’s version of the ground-breaking, open source "Profiles Research Networking Software" that was developed under the supervision of Griffin M Weber, MD, PhD, with support from Grant Number 1 UL1 RR025758-01 to <a href="http://catalyst.harvard.edu/" target="_new">Harvard Catalyst: The Harvard Clinical and Translational Science Center</a> from the National Center for Research Resources and support from Harvard University and its affiliated academic healthcare centers.</p>

<p>Profiles Research Networking Software is available as an <a href="http://connects.catalyst.harvard.edu/Profiles/about/default.aspx?tab=open" target="_blank">open source platform</a> for institutions seeking a web-based means of facilitating collaboration among their academic researchers. </p>  

